  "title": "(Up $3000) Contract Lab Technician (6 Months) #HCGT",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>-         \nPreparing of samples for\nanalysis and testing</p><p>-         \nAnalysis of samples using\ndifferent methods and instruments</p><p>-         \nHelp to maintain the\nsystem</p><p>-         \nRecording data and doing\nreports</p><p>-         \nFollow proper laboratory safety guidelines\nand protocols, including the proper handling and disposal of hazardous materials</p><p>-         \nOther ad-hoc duties</p><p>Job Requirement:</p><p>-         \nMinimum Diploma in\nChemistry/Chemical Engineering or related fields</p><p>-         \nInternship experience\nwill be highly preferred</p><p>-         \nGood communication skills</p><p>-         \nTeam player</p><p>-         \nMinimum commitment of 6\nmonths</p><p>All qualified\napplicants, please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>Tricia Celestine Goh (R1981653)<br />\nRecruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No.\n199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>",
